<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #10B981;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #FEF2F2;
            border-left: 4px solid #EF4444;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Password Changed Successfully</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>

        <p>This email confirms that your password for your TCG Marketplace account was successfully changed.</p>

        <p>If you made this change, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <strong>Didn't change your password?</strong><br>
            If you didn't make this change, please contact our support team immediately to secure your account.
        </div>

        <p>For security, we recommend:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Using a unique password that you don't use anywhere else</li>
            <li>Using a strong password with letters, numbers, and symbols</li>
            <li>Changing your password regularly</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any concerns, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 TCG Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
